reviews.text: Ordered the two people set dinner plus garlic bread and avocado salad. I did not know the pizza comes in small size, but with the rice and potato that we ordered, this size of pizza was good enough for three people to share. The avocado salad and garlic bread were unexpectedly good. Will come back to try their new pizza.

Excellent western restaurant for neighborhood families. Week end traffic is much higher than week days. High value food with acceptable food quality. We ordered set dinner for four pax which was more than sufficient for 5 adults and a child. Seating is spacious. Unfortunately everyone agreed the tongue burning soup with puff pastry is much tastier then the lukewarm cream soup. Hope the restaurant can improve next time!
Overcrowded and understaffed during lunch hours. Fast food at best.
Comfortable place to go for afternoon Tea Sets. Good selections of Mini pizza and small portion food  offered inclusive of hot and cold drink at reasonable price.
Pleasant environment but a bit expensive.
